  <summary date="2022-09-08T18:13:33Z" status="Introduced in House">Thirty-Two Hour Workweek Act

This bill shortens the standard workweek under federal law from 40 hours to 32 hours over a three-year phase in period. It also requires specified overtime pay for workdays longer than eight hours.</summary>
